    <body>
      <div type="mūlam" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV17">
<l>pāṅkuṇar vaiyuṟa virantukuṟai yuṟutalu</l>
<l>māṅkavaṉ viṉātalu matiyuṭa ṉākkalun</l>
<l>tuṇitaluñ cēṭpaṭa niṟuttaluñ cuṭṭiya</l>
<l>taṟiyē ṉaṟivaṉ maṟaiyē leṉṟaluṅ</l>
<l>kuṟiyā kūṟalum paṭaittaṉa moḻitalu</l>
<l>mariyā ḷeṉṟalu nīkū ṟeṉṟalu</l>
<l>nakaikoṇ ṭāṟṟalu nakāturai yeṉṟalum</l>
<l>periyīr yāmataṟ kiyaiyē meṉṟaluṅ</l>
<l>kaiyuṟai yeḷimai kāṭṭalu meyyuṟa</l>
<l>ovvā teṉṟalu mavaṇilai yuṇarntu</l>
<l>koḷkuva ṉeṉṟalu maṭaṉmā kūṟalu</l>
<l>maṟṟatu vilakkaluṅ kaiyuṟai kōṭalum</l>
<l>viḻaiya vuṇarttalu nāṇoṭu nīṅkalum</l>
<l>valitākac collik kuṟainayap pittalun</l>
<l>taḻīik kōṭalun taḻaiyēṟ pittaluṅ</l>
<l>kaiyuṟai yetirntamai meypeṟa vicaittalum</l>
<l>virumpiṭa muraittaluṅ kuṟiyoṭu nīṅkalum</l>
<l>puṉaintu nilaiyalu nilaimai kūṟalum</l>
<l>pāṅkikoṇ ṭikattalum pakaṟkuṟi yākum.</l>
</lg>
